title: Anne Van Parijs
text: Anne Van Parijs (born 14 April 1944) is a Belgian former <a href="Swimming%20%28sport%29">swimmer</a>. She competed in the <a href="Swimming%20at%20the%201960%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20100%20metre%20backstroke">women's 100 metre backstroke</a> at the <a href="1960%20Summer%20Olympics">1960 Summer Olympics</a>.
